{"tid":2513460,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[Offer二揀一] Big 4定EO?","createTime":"2021-05-02T13:51:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T14:41:04.000Z","uid":234845,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4ab0ea55244c83e9e3187ab51159beb42a87c780","tid":2513460,"uid":234845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T13:51:55.000Z","msg":"上年9月開始係Big 4 IS audit做, 去到近排有EO offer, 諗緊轉唔轉好<br />\n<br />\n因為而家Big 4環境好似已經唔係好似以前咁識呼吸就升到manager, 而且工時又長, 我知政府工一定會俾人屌, 但真係鐵飯碗, 起薪又高(雖然之後加幅少過Big 4), 又多返好多私人時間<br />\n<br />\n但政府工又好似好悶同冇一班差唔多年紀嘅同事咁, 同埋聽講而家開始又好似升慢咗, 而且啲福利其實冇想像中咁好, 有冇EO巴絲可以講下入面工作情況同大概幾耐會升到5,6萬到？最好有巴絲放棄政府offer留係私人/係私人轉去政府可以分享吓原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申冇諗過移民"},{"pid":"b215126d061b717cfff4f024799db35db6da7b90","tid":2513460,"uid":367785,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T13:52:30.000Z","msg":"Are you fucking kidding me"},{"pid":"7a7274599eab0d964c0aa2091432c30a12caef3e","tid":2513460,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T13:54:10.000Z","msg":"轉去external audit咪可以識呼吸都升到m"},{"pid":"81c6f180458f0583134589724286d2889d0d9f3a","tid":2513460,"uid":341807,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T13:55:27.000Z","msg":"EO for sure,big 4 wok到日日3 am,wokload 係EO 2倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c3218761723ecb2f10721f7110fa5d6d48d894","tid":2513460,"uid":59222,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9cc3e3fc92dfca0c469c2f0c89c76f66e0d02c3","tid":2513460,"uid":15880,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:02:45.000Z","msg":"得閒射下EMAIL 就一日，入職都３萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nEO 一百個先收一個咁都要諗"},{"pid":"2bcbd6e927e18a1ae2ea0da8f6f06b134300dcc6","tid":2513460,"uid":20584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:11:48.000Z","msg":"大佬你假膠定真心問<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc4f63dd272a29f75a71857672b6545e0759caa4","tid":2513460,"uid":364770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:14:38.000Z","msg":"Of course eo la"},{"pid":"d0ca6bb1eb4fa7c060ae8a8b05208b28a0e3d477","tid":2513460,"uid":89249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:23:08.000Z","msg":"自問有料唔甘心天花板低嘅咪big4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係好想捱想安安穩穩就eo,但你預咗做eo如果他日移民就比較難搵到差唔多人工嘅工"},{"pid":"5ac2e0f9b9df41bc7c684dcaad2af8e8b4c0811e","tid":2513460,"uid":234845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:25:37.000Z","msg":"見好多人都話EO<br />\n但我覺得EO係贏頭輸尾(人工方面)<br />\n不過我又唔敢肯定EO輸尾又會輸幾多<br />\n同埋工作時數方面會唔會compensate到<br />\n加上我又比較重視工作環境同埋同事關係 (eg 有冇老屎忽/差唔多年紀嘅同事)<br />\n所以先咁struggle<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7673005adc4b4ffbc2cb6d508d86345e771b50d4","tid":2513460,"uid":362827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:29:15.000Z","msg":"樓主 big4工作時間係點？"},{"pid":"93d19ab74f213709a63a14869a84d8a1f302e556","tid":2513460,"uid":35190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:31:41.000Z","msg":"Eo"},{"pid":"6bfd93480b08e8df3bb24d3214cf5f08559ab8b2","tid":2513460,"uid":73492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:31:51.000Z","msg":"講工作舒適度 eo好d 唔洗解釋<br />\n<br />\n講金錢回報 兩者差不多 EO穩定上中產 audit可能無賺咁多 又可能升到好高級搵勁多 所以拉中位數黎比 差不多<br />\n<br />\n講滿足感 兩者差不多 eo 有d位係廢位 有d位搞活動都有意義 audit 做數有d好有趣 有d job好悶 得個check字<br />\n<br />\n講移民 audit好d 唔洗解釋<br />\n<br />\n講言論自由 audit好d 入左eo唔比再講政治 audit仲可以講政治 至少仲有一部分言論自由<br />\n<br />\n講穩定 eo好d 世界大亂經濟再差 公務員都唔會失業 audit都成日話大行可能會職業轉移去大陸 或者經濟太差 in-house audit真係可以比人炒 但公務員永無炒人<br />\n<br />\n講到尾 都係睇你要乜 你想要平凡中產生活 即係eo囉<br />\n你想移民 即係audit囉 <br />\n<br />\n你問你自己 打份工係想要乜 就知應該做邊份工<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每年真係一車車big4人轉EO"},{"pid":"55f80d5d5ed3f31a75ba4f688d7591442f7f84b9","tid":2513460,"uid":9253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7673005adc4b4ffbc2cb6d508d86345e771b50d4","tid":2513460,"uid":362827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:29:15.000Z","msg":"樓主 big4工作時間係點？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:32:41.000Z","msg":"audit有番工無放工？"},{"pid":"85ee7385595a588f2c99f28fe8ef446613274795","tid":2513460,"uid":73270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ab0ea55244c83e9e3187ab51159beb42a87c780","tid":2513460,"uid":234845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T13:51:55.000Z","msg":"上年9月開始係Big 4 IS audit做, 去到近排有EO offer, 諗緊轉唔轉好<br />\n<br />\n因為而家Big 4環境好似已經唔係好似以前咁識呼吸就升到manager, 而且工時又長, 我知政府工一定會俾人屌, 但真係鐵飯碗, 起薪又高(雖然之後加幅少過Big 4), 又多返好多私人時間<br />\n<br />\n但政府工又好似好悶同冇一班差唔多年紀嘅同事咁, 同埋聽講而家開始又好似升慢咗, 而且啲福利其實冇想像中咁好, 有冇EO巴絲可以講下入面工作情況同大概幾耐會升到5,6萬到？最好有巴絲放棄政府offer留係私人/係私人轉去政府可以分享吓原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申冇諗過移民"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:34:39.000Z","msg":"Fg?"},{"pid":"0d09fa90747eb220039e43e764abad637de2edfe","tid":2513460,"uid":241804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:36:00.000Z","msg":"無諗住移民想安定嘅話，就eo<br />\n<br />\n無諗住移民但想跳出去嘅話，就big4<br />\n<br />\n想移民嘅話，都係big4<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />